name: csa
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "1.22.0" %}

package:
    name: csa
    version: {{ version }}

source:
    fn: v{{ version }}.tar.gz
    url: https://github.com/sakov/csa-c/archive/v{{ version }}.tar.gz
    sha256: b6d6ebeea146e09fc7aef827a3a3b22b7af674c2f0c67169c2275237e54c0c02

build:
    number: 1
    skip: True  # [win]

test:
    commands:
        - csabathy -V
        - conda inspect linkages -n _test csa  # [not win]

about:
    home: https://github.com/sakov/csa-c
    license: BSD 2-Clause
    summary: 'Cubic Spline Approximation.'

extra:
    recipe-maintainers:
        - ocefpaf
